I used p5.js to recreate Kanye West's iconic live performance of his song Runaway on a drum machine. I utilised different libraries, youtube videos and websites to help bring the project to life. I also can't forget to mention my lecturer Conor Brennan who was a great help throughout the process.

My sources:
 //Pixel Array Background Change: https://youtu.be/nMUMZ5YRxHI
  //Refresher On Creating OScillating Waves: https://youtu.be/GvwPwIUSYqE
  //Conor's Oscillator class and For Loops: https://editor.p5js.org/CB/sketches/tz3yhe8UX
  //Getting The Sounds To Play With Buttons (16:36-24:24): https://youtu.be/Iep6ZWtf4o8
  //Changing Font: https://youtu.be/L-aTxyWmaTU
  //Changing Volume with sliders: https://youtu.be/Pn1g1wjxl_0
